item.title: Van Halen Trivia II
item.description:
Featuring a live trivia showdown with Patreon supporters going head‑to‑head on all things Van Halen. It’s a high‑energy milestone episode hosted by Mark Camire and Corey Morrissette, making it a spirited way to mark their 200th episode milestone.


So if you’re into Van Halen lore, trivia battles, and fan participation, Episode 200 sounds like a blast — worth checking out whether you’re a super-fan or just curious about the fun... Feed: https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/6572121fcc2cf30012848ae1

item.title: [INTERVIEW] Finding Your Voice Over a Decade of Creating with Lostboycrow
item.description: We sat down with Lostboycrow, also known as Chris Blair, to explore his creative journey over the past decade. Chris shares how personal growth and life experiences have shaped his music. We deep dive into his experiences with the ever-changing music platforms, how getting into acting changed his perspective on his music, and so much more. Learn more about your ad choices. Visit megaphone.fm/adchoices Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/NSR5664838084
